<li>Shannon, Fred A. <i>The Farmer's Last Frontier: 1860-1897</i> (1945) survey of economic history <a href="http://www.questia.com/PM.qst?a=o&amp;d=59123553" class="external text" title="http://www.questia.com/PM.qst?a=o&amp;d=59123553" rel="nofollow">online edition</a></li>
<li>Smythe, Ted Curtis; <i>The Gilded Age Press, 1865-1900</i> Praeger. 2003. [online edition]</li>
</ul>
