<ul>
<li>Ashton, Susanna M. "The King's Men, or A Parable of Democratic Authorship." Chapter 2 of <i>Collaborators in Literary America, 1870-1920.</i> New York: Palgrave Macmillan, 2003.</li>
</ul>
